description.narrative: UNICEF advocated the government and parliamentarians to adopt the multisectoral nutrition policy to raise the level of nutrition coordination body to a supra-minister level and to increase government funding for nutrition. UNICEF, as the lead of the nutrition partners group, coordinated the nutrition emergency response. UNICEF supported the MoH to strengthen the routine nutrition information system, to conduct the 2019 national nutrition survey and to conduct a rapid nutrition survey in 6 municipalities hosting the largest number of displaced people. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
